<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
@EM{{@HI{{na}}}} is a sentence ending particle with a number of uses.
</p>

@BGRNDSTART{{}}

@BGRND{{}}
<p>
Some uses of @EM{{@HI{{na}}}} are most often used by men:
<ul>
<li> indicates emotion
<li> asks for agreement
<li> indicates <a href="grammar-verb-use-of-imperative-prohibitive.html">prohibition</a>
</ul>
</p>

@BGRND{{}}
<p>
Some uses of @EM{{@HI{{na}}}} can be used by either men or women:
<ul>
<li> softens the effect of an assertion
<li> softens a request or a command
</ul>
</p>

@BGRNDEND{{}}

